{"tid":1819862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"活禾特個人收入排英超第1  熱刺主席列維排第2","createTime":"2020-01-11T07:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T08:07:51.000Z","uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0f3b8ae292ef58acb88b47b90832481cac1522","tid":1819862,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"儘管<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯執行副主席活禾特飽受球迷批評，被認為運作球隊不佳，但他在個人收入方面仍是英超同行中最高的</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  據《泰晤士報》的數據披露，<span style=\"color: red;\">活禾特在曼聯的年收入是310萬英鎊</span>（約合2800萬人民幣），是英超球會高管中收入最高的。排在<span style=\"color: red;\">第二的是熱刺主席列維，年收入是300萬英鎊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  另外從2018年6月到2019年6月，曼聯一年支付給12名董事成員的工資總額為680萬英鎊，這其中就包括費格遜、波比-查爾頓等球會顧問或大使。<br />\n<br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\">活禾特對球會的主要貢獻在場外，曼聯已經拿到了超過五十個全球或區域知名品牌的贊助。過去一年裡，曼聯球會經營的純利潤（收入減去支出）達到了1900萬英鎊</span>，不過由於今季沒有進入歐冠盃，這一數字在今年可能會有所下降。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac50dd3711bca26f377536d76fe373d0a9742b4","tid":1819862,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"檯底"},{"pid":"814a1416bd407f466dec59d931c486124364a6e5","tid":1819862,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f231b2f656878c9aa8961ff5f8005782478c14c","tid":1819862,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:03:06.000Z","msg":"（約合2800萬人民幣）<br />\n<br />\n睇支那網？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f49d9a4b187c19538976c164e5a81f1eb196f29","tid":1819862,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f231b2f656878c9aa8961ff5f8005782478c14c","tid":1819862,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:03:06.000Z","msg":"（約合2800萬人民幣）<br />\n<br />\n睇支那網？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji